Map Created by Skope and GamerInTheDark


CT\'s must alive and get through the map.
T\'s got weapons (AwP and Elite), they must kill the CT\'s.

If a CT Finnished the Map he can do 3 things: -They can press a kill button.
                                                                 - If they press another button the ct will teleportet to
                                                                   some other Buttons and the T must came trough the
                                                                   Traps (the Buttons activate the Trap\'s), this is working
                                                                   like a deahtrun map
                                                                 - The ct can teleport the t into a room and than they
                                                                   can knife :)


There are 26 Player Slots. 24 Ct Slots and 2 T Slots.

Warning: This map need NoBlock! If a server do not have it the T\'s and Ct\'s will stuck if you press any
              Button!



We hope you have fun with our Map!
